body:
Job requirements: 
University degree, preferably in Economics;
English knowledge both spoken and written; Banking experience is needed; 
Customer-care oriented, with good communication skills, able to solve promptly and professionally the customers' requests;
Good selling and negotiation skills also requested;
Dynamic and flexible person, enthusiastic, with initiative and a pro-active attitude;
Qualification as bank assurance agent would be a plus. 

Key responsibilities:
 The nominees will interact directly with customers, open and administrate their accounts and ensure information on the bank's products and services; she/ he will promote products and services to clients, analyse and manage applications for card issuance. All applications will be treated in strictest confidence. Only short-listed candidates will be contacted for an interview.
